2. 将其他字段的值转换成适当的数据类型（例如，将颜色字段转换为小写字母），并且根据需求对这些字段进行排序；

BEGIN
    SELECT $1, $2, $3, $4
        | SELECT _get_column_values( $1, $2, ARRAY[$3] )
        | ORDER BY _sort_order($4);
$$ LANGUAGE SQL;

CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION _get_column_values ( NAME, NAME, NAME[] ) AS $$
BEGIN
    DECLARE @columns NAME[];
    SELECT _get_column_names($1)
            INTO ARRAY[$2], ARRAY[$3];
    SELECT _cast_to_data_type(ARRAY[$1], ARRAY[$2])
            INTO @columns[] AS $1
                   ORDER BY $2[][COLUMN_POSITION()];
    SELECT _convert_characters($3, $1);
END;
$$ LANGUAGE plpgsql;

CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION _sort_order ( NAME[] ) AS $$
BEGIN
    DECLARE $1 NAME[][];
    IF ARRAY[$1][0] IS NULL
            OR $1[0] NOT LIKE _$1[]
            OR _cast_to_data_type($1[0], _get_column_data_types()) != $1[0]
            OR ARRAY[$1][1] IS NULL
                OR ARRAY[$1][2] IS NULL
                OR _is_null($1[3])
                OR ARRAY[$1][4] IS NULL

BEGIN
    SELECT $1, $2, $3, $4
        | SELECT _get_column_values( $1, $2, ARRAY[$3] )
        | ORDER BY _sort_order($4);
$$ LANGUAGE SQL;

    SELECT _get_column_names($1)
